[h3 id=BoostingDownwards 
	" Boosting downwards
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Every unspin boosts Samus down 5px, so unspinnning every other frame give you an instant ~2.6px/frame velocity. So when falling less than 3 blocks distance and moving forwards isn't a concern, boosting downwards is faster than normally falling.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Here are a few uses:
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=FallThroughCrumbleBlocksFaster 
	" Fall through crumble blocks faster 
	[img class=embedright mw-100 src=https://files.tasvideos.org/gameresources/gba/metroidfusion/FusionDrop.gif 
	]img
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Falling through crumble blocks (as shown) involve distances less than 3 blocks, so boosting downwards through them is faster than normally falling.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=FallDownWaterQuicker 
	" Fall down water quicker
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"When falling in water, your downwards velocity is automatically set to 1.5px per frame, meaning boosting downwards is 1.75 times faster.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=CorollaxTrick 
	" Corollax trick
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"The Corollax trick is when you duck as soon as you hit the ground to store a shinespark after speed boosting off a ledge. You can also jump and do the Corollax trick. To do this you have to jump without spinning by pressing:
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Frame 1: Nothing
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"Frame 2: Jump
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"Frame 3: Jump + forward
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Holding forward until you duck.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Here are a few uses:
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=FightBoxFaster 
	" Fight BOX faster
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Speed boost to the wrecked room after super missiles, perform a jumping Corollax trick as far as possible, and run to the point where the ground starts rumbling 
	[a id=r1 
	]a
	[sup 
		"[
		[a href=#1 
			"1
		]a
		"]
	]sup
	", then spark back to the start of the room. (
	[a href=http://dehacked.2y.net/microstorage.php/info/551257223/Pre-BOX%20spark.vbm rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"reference vbm
	]a
	")
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[a class=intlink href=/Users/Profile/P.JBoy 
		"P.JBoy
	]a
	": I've tried and failed sparking into box's room itself, if anyone else wants to have a go, 
	[a href=http://dehacked.2y.net/microstorage.php/info/1772566797/Failed%20%286%20frames%29%20BOX%20Spark.vbm rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"here
	]a
	"'s my attempt.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=EngageNocSaXFaster 
	" Engage NOC SA-X faster
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"In the energy tank room before the SA-X room, perform the jumping Corollax trick so that you land to the left of the energy tank, bomb the passage, grab the energy tank, travel the passage, shoot the door, and spark through. This only works if you grab the energy tank, because your shine timer stops while the bomb still explodes. (
	[a href=http://dehacked.2y.net/microstorage.php/info/741956366/Pre-NOC%20SA-X%20spark.vbm rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"reference vbm
	]a
	")
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=GettingIceMissilesBackwards 
	" Getting ice missiles backwards
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"After unlocking security level 3, go to the left edge of the room.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"Run right 2 rooms. You should be able to run through the Kago and perform the jumping Corollax trick at the end of the ledge.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"Run to the save room and spark into the right stairs. In the next room, perform the jumping Corollax trick again into the next room.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"In this room, spin jump far enough to the right (in order to avoid the wall above) and spark to the top. (
	[a href=http://dehacked.2y.net/microstorage.php/info/203800349/Ice-missiles%20backwards.vbm rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"reference vbm
	]a
	")
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=SparkUpTheArcShaft 
	" Spark up the ARC shaft
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"In the first ARC room, go to the left edge, run to the ARC shaft room, perform the jumping Corollax trick, go to the ladder, and spark up. (
	[a href=http://dehacked.2y.net/microstorage.php/info/1513943241/ARC%20ladder%20spark.vbm rel=noopener external nofollow 
		"reference vbm
	]a
	")
	$LF
]div
